               CM Creator Overview

CM (Compartmentalized Model) Creator is an early-stage Computer-Aided
Design (CAD) program for creation, analyses, prototyping, and export
of Compartmentalized Models. A Compartmentalized Model (CModel) is a
digital description of the exterior and interior of a subdivided
structure such as a building, ship, or other habitat.

CM Creator is designed specifically for efficient modeling of the
interior portion of a CModel. Efficiency is achieved by new features
such as automatic creation of compartment and space descriptions
(after interior partitions are defined). The program can also compute
geometric properties of exterior and interior surfaces, compartments,
and spaces; and automatically create data classification systems for
organizing and displaying the geometric properties.

